# Tripistry ‚Äî Travel Package Comparison Platform

COS 221 Practical Assignment 5 | University of Pretoria | 2026

---

## Overview

Tripistry is a full-stack web application that allows travellers to browse, compare and book
travel packages from multiple verified travel agencies. Travel agencies can create and manage
packages, view bookings and read customer reviews through a dedicated agency dashboard.

The application is built with PHP (OOP), MariaDB and vanilla JavaScript, and is served
through Apache via XAMPP.

