## API Reference

The REST API is located at `http://localhost/COS221-Tripistry/api.php`.

All requests use `POST` with a JSON body containing at minimum a `type` field.

### Public Endpoints (no authentication required)

| Type | Parameters | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `Register` | `username`, `email`, `password`, `user_type`, `agency_name`*, `registration_number`* | Register a new user |
| `Login` | `email`, `password` | Log in and receive an API key |
| `GetPackages` | `dest_id`?, `min_price`?, `max_price`?, `search`?, `sort_by`?, `order`? | Browse all active packages |
| `GetPackage` | `package_id` | Get full details for one package |
| `GetReviews` | `package_id` | Get all reviews for a package |

### Traveller Endpoints (api_key required)

| Type | Parameters | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `GetBookings` | `api_key` | Get all bookings for the logged-in traveller |
| `AddReview` | `api_key`, `package_id`, `rating`, `comment`? | Submit a review |
| `AddFavourite` | `api_key`, `package_id` | Save a package to favourites |
| `RemoveFavourite` | `api_key`, `package_id` | Remove a package from favourites |
| `GetFavourites` | `api_key` | Get all favourited packages |

### Agency Endpoints (api_key required, travel_agent only)

| Type | Parameters | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `GetAgencyPackages` | `api_key` | Get all packages for the logged-in agency |
| `GetAgencyBookings` | `api_key` | Get all bookings for agency packages |
| `GetAgencyReviews` | `api_key` | Get all reviews for agency packages |
| `CreatePackage` | `api_key`, `title`, `dest_id`, `price`, `quantity`, `expiry_date`, `status`, `description`?, `is_group`?, `min_group_size`?, `max_group_size`? | Create a new package |
| `UpdatePackage` | `api_key`, `package_id`, + same as CreatePackage | Edit an existing package |
| `DeletePackage` | `api_key`, `package_id` | Delete a package |

`*` Required for agency registration only
`?` Optional parameter

